    (rev "K")
    (company "Steve Griffing PE(CSE) CISSP-ISSEP CPP")
    (comment 1 "PocketBeagle 2 (AM6232) Communications/Payload Cape — CN node")
    (comment 2 "90x60mm 4-layer  SiK 915MHz · RFM95W LoRa · WL1837MOD WiFi/BT · RCRS-49 · ATF16V8BQL CPLD · W25Q128JV NOR · μSD · SLB9670 TPM")
